// it-format: 1.0
title: Vendor Onboarding Form
summary: Required for all new suppliers and subcontractors
meta: | type: form | ref: FORM-VEND-001 | version: 2.1 | date: 2026-06-01 | theme: corporate

section: Vendor Identity
input: Legal entity name | key: entity_name | type: text | required: yes
input: Trading name (if different) | key: trading_name | type: text
input: Country of incorporation | key: country | type: select | options: QA, SA, AE, KW, BH, OM, GB, US, IN, OTHER
input: Commercial Registration number | key: cr_number | type: text | required: yes
input: VAT / Tax registration number | key: vat_number | type: text | show-if: country == QA
input: Date of incorporation | key: incorporation_date | type: date | required: yes

section: Contact Details
input: Primary contact name | key: contact_name | type: text | required: yes
input: Primary contact email | key: contact_email | type: text | required: yes
input: Primary contact phone | key: contact_phone | type: text | required: yes
input: Registered office address | key: address | type: text | required: yes

section: Banking Details
input: Bank name | key: bank_name | type: text | required: yes
input: IBAN | key: iban | type: text | required: yes
input: Swift / BIC | key: swift | type: text | required: yes
input: Account currency | key: currency | type: select | options: QAR, USD, GBP, EUR | required: yes

section: Commercial Terms
input: Standard payment terms preferred | key: payment_terms | type: select | options: Net 15, Net 30, Net 45, Net 60
input: Estimated annual contract value (QAR) | key: estimated_value | type: number
input: Estimated annual contract value (QAR) — confirmed | key: value_confirmed | type: number | compute: estimated_value * 1

section: Documents
input: Commercial Registration certificate (PDF) | key: cr_pdf | type: attachment | required: yes
input: VAT certificate (PDF) | key: vat_pdf | type: attachment | show-if: vat_number != ""
input: ISO or quality certification (PDF) | key: iso_pdf | type: attachment
input: Bank letter confirming account details (PDF) | key: bank_letter | type: attachment | required: yes

section: Declaration
input: I confirm all information is accurate and complete | key: declaration | type: select | options: Yes, No | required: yes
input: Authorised signatory name | key: signatory | type: text | required: yes
input: Submission date | key: submission_date | type: date | required: yes
